COPY public.page_aboutpageseo_translation (id, language_code, seo_title, meta_description, banner_title, banner_description, master_id, content, subtitle, title, faq_description, faq_subtitle, faq_title) FROM stdin;
1	en	About us - Dr. Cengiz Sarolu	We believe that every patient wants and deserves a successful pregnancy in the first cycle of treatment. That's why we recommend that you take all the necessary tests to ensure this result.	About us	<p><span style="font-size:20px">There are many things to consider <strong>when planning IVF treatment. </strong>As well as good success rates, excellent expertise, and personal care. Another important factor to consider is price. When it comes to IVF treatment, costs can be confusing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>&ldquo;We&rsquo;re on a mission to make IVF more affordable and accessible in Turkiye.&rdquo;</strong></span></p>	1	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:22px">We believe that every patient wants and deserves a successful pregnancy in the first cycle of treatment. That&#39;s why we recommend that you take all the necessary tests to ensure this result.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:20px"><span style="color:#203240">The main reasons our treatments are lower cost include:</span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px"> &nbsp;Specialist protocols</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp; &nbsp;Simplified patient journey</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px"> &nbsp;No unnecessary tests</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px"></span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;No unnecessary scans</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px"> </span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;No unproven, add-ons</span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:18px"> &nbsp;No unnecessary appointments</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">Clarity of pricing</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">Typically, there are many known factors involved in IVF treatment, but many clinics fail to include them in advance. Instead, they&rsquo;re listed as &ldquo;extras&rdquo;, which can be confusing and leave you paying much more than you expected.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">However, we will include all known items necessary for the completion of your treatment cycle as part of a clear package cost. That&#39;s why another clinic&#39;s website may have a lower IVF treatment price. There are some unknowns when planning treatment protocols, such as medications and immunology tests, but your doctor will discuss these with you in detail beforehand and only recommend a treatment plan that we believe will give you the best chance of success.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">Compare plans</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">We offer women-friendly treatment that results in better health outcomes for mothers and babies. Our pioneering approach focuses on egg quality, not egg quantity.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:22px">We&#39;re committed to protecting the health of women and babies in the long term, and to being able to look back and say, </span></span><span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:22px"><em><strong>&quot;We did the right thing.&rdquo;</strong></em></span></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#203240"><span style="font-size:22px">We have a responsibility not only for the present, but also for the future.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#e72254"><span style="font-size:22px"><em><strong>We build families.</strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," style="height:356px; width:300px" /><br />\r\n<span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Dr. Cengiz SAGIROGLU</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254">Founder and Medical Director</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">About Clinic</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Our Clinic for Assisted Reproduction</strong> is a specialist clinic dedicated to the diagnosis and treatment of infertility and fertility disorders. We offer a comprehensive range of treatment methods and additional techniques that not only improve success rates, but also enhance the comfort of our patients.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">Our clinic was established in 2019 and is based on tradition, experience, and continual education in the field of reproductive medicine. <strong>Our founder, Dr. Cengiz SAGIROGLU,</strong> has gained extensive experience at the most reputable centers specializing in obstetrics and reproductive medicine, both in Turkiye and abroad. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">Thanks to his professional expertise, we have been able to build a modern center which has precise technical equipment, sophisticated processes, and effectively trained personnel. We believe that these robust foundations will enable us to provide our patients with not only advanced care, but also with comfort and safety in a friendly environment.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240"><em>Our mission<strong> </strong></em></span><span style="color:#e72254"><em><strong>&ldquo;to make IVF more affordable and accessible in Turkiye.&rdquo;</strong></em></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#203240"><em>Our goal is<strong> </strong></em></span><span style="color:#e72254"><em><strong>&ldquo;to guide you towards a new life.&rdquo;</strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">Our Vision</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">We are proud to participate in international clinical surveys and studies, which contribute to the overall development of the field of assisted reproduction. Our patients are given the opportunity to closely monitor the progress of their therapy, gain a deeper understanding of the laboratory processes and fully participate in every step and decision made throughout their journey to the desired goal. The clinic&#39;s equipment at our clinic has been designed to enable every stage of the journey to be visually monitored. This begins with the egg collection, continues with quality assessment, and extends to the cultivation of the embryo stage. Based on this strategy and vision, we aim to provide our patients with as much information as possible about infertility treatment, to help them make informed decisions and contribute to their peace of mind.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">How we define success</span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">Our personalized treatment protocols deliver successful outcomes whilst protecting the health of women and babies.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:18px">There are several factors that influence the success rate. At our clinic, we assess success not only by the outcome, but also by improvements 