1	en	Why us?		Why us?	<p>As your family grows up, it is an important decision to choose the doctor you will entrust to the care of two people - you and your baby - and who will deliver your baby.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>	Endless effort to boost your fertility	Take your first step with US	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px">Every patient is put on the best possible treatment plan for the highest chance of success. That process starts with our thoughtful and thorough screening, which is focused on understanding you and your fertility health. Then when you&rsquo;re ready to start your fertility treatment, you&rsquo;ll find our state-of-the-art clinic and laboratories have everything you need to maximize your chance of success and minimize your time to a successful pregnancy.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:24px"><span style="color:#203240"><em><strong>&ldquo;It&rsquo;s how we make the impossible, </strong></em></span><span style="color:#e72254"><em><strong>possible.&rdquo;</strong></em></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align:center"><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2 style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#e72254"><em>Put your trust in US</em></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">Fertility experience of over 15 years</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We are very proud to have one of the most experienced and respected fertility consultants in the field. <span style="color:#203240">&nbsp;</span><a href="https://jineartivf.bcmtest.com/en/about-doctor/"><span style="color:#203240"><strong>Dr. Cengiz SAGIROGLU</strong></span></a> works daily on patient outcomes and pathways and is committed to the ethos of finding fertility solutions for everyone. &nbsp;His dedication to each patient leaves no stone unturned and combines the best knowledge. &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">We&#39;re transparent about our costs</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe that transparency is a critical factor for patients planning their finances. Our aim is to build trust from the outset with full clarity on costs. Our fertility treatment is highly personalized, with a variety of bespoke treatment plans, which means that comparing costs with another patient is not always helpful. The price lists on the internet can also be confusing. However, we include ALL of these in our package prices as there are some standard costs that are essential to every patient&#39;s journey. So, we don&#39;t always have the lowest advertised price. But we are the most transparent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><u><span style="font-size:20px"><em><a href="https://drsagiroglu.com/en/pricing/"><span style="color:#203240"><strong>Please see the full list of all our prices in the Treatment Fees section.</strong></span></a></em></span></u><a href="https://drsagiroglu.com/en/pricing/"><u><span style="font-size:20px"><em><span style="color:#203240">&nbsp;</span><span style="color:#e72254">(Click here to get more information)</span></em></span></u></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">In-depth research for you</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>We believe in leaving no stone unturned when preparing for a successful pregnancy. &nbsp;That&#39;s why, before we set out a treatment plan, we take the time to fully understand your fertility health and medical history. As many patients come to us after unsuccessful cycles elsewhere, you&#39;ll be reassured by our approach of re-evaluating everything to find the best treatment path for success. We meet daily to share knowledge and find the best way forward.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">Why us?</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Combining exceptional care and expertise with state-of-the-art facilities. Our Clinic is dedicated to helping patients become parents. Our approach to fertility treatment is comprehensive and up to date, leaving no aspect unexplored.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-size:22px"><span style="color:#203240">We have a high </span><span style="color:#e72254">success rates</span></span></strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:18px">We accept all patients because we believe there&#39;s always a fertility option, and this drive to succeed is reflected in our success rates. We&#39;re proud to say that whatever your age, ethnicity, or medical condition, we have the leading success rates in the Turkiye.</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><span style="color:#e72254"><em><span style="font-size:22px">Our aim is simple;&nbsp;</span></em></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#203240"><em><span style="font-size:22px">&ldquo;To do everything possible to achieve a live birth in the first cycle&rdquo;.</span></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center"><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">Here are a few highlights...</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our pregnancy rate per embryo transfer is now 59% across all age groups (and 50% per embryo transferred). This compares with a national average of 23%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /><br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\nOur main goal is to help more of our patients have successful pregnancies. We operate to the highest international standards in reproductive technology. This is what sets us apart and enables our success.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:20px"><u><em><a href="https://drsagiroglu.com/en/success-rates/"><span style="color:#203240"><strong>Find out more about the </strong></span><span style="color:#e72254"><strong>success rates.</strong></span></a></em></u></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><br />\r\n<span style="color:#203240">More reasons why patients choose us:</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">We are always ready to help and treat</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We go further than any other clinic in Turkiye to increase your chances of a successful pregnancy by finding and treating the specific problems that may be preventing you from conceiving or carrying to term.<br />\r\nThroughout your treatment, you&#39;ll see the same doctor<br />\r\nWe understand that it&#39;s comforting to see familiar faces when you come to the hospital, so you&#39;ll always receive attentive and thorough care from the same doctor.<br />\r\nWe offer a wide range of finance options<br />\r\nFertility treatment can be physically, emotionally, and financially challenging. Our funding options can help make the journey a little easier.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">Our facilities</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">3D ultrasound and analysis</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We use a diagnostic imaging technique that provides a detailed picture of internal organs and invaluable information for diagnosing and treating fertility problems in women. We also offer the latest ultrasound equipment, including early pregnancy scans and 3D/5D scans of your baby.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">Endometrial analysis</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>This allows us to carry out a thorough analysis of the specific problems that lead to implantation failure. This allows us to recommend the safest and most effective method of conception for you and your family.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">Cutting edge, yet comfortable</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Our state-of-the-art clinic is fully equipped to provide world-class fertility testing and treatment in an environment that always feels safe and comfortable. Take a quick tour of our facilities below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">Our in-house laboratory</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>From hormone levels to ovarian reserve, we can test, analyze, and quickly provide you with detailed results and the best next steps thanks to our laboratory.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4><span style="color:#203240">Genetic testing tools</span></h4>\r\n\r\n<p>We use the latest techniques to check for genetic abnormalities to ensure that only the healthiest eggs and embryos are used in your fertility treatment - increasing the pregnancy rate, reducing the risk of miscarriage, and decreasing the risk of a child being born with a genetic abnormality.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><br />\r\n<span style="color:#203240">Learn more with our upcoming webinars</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>During the fertility process, it&#39;s normal to feel anxious, sad, or even overwhelmed at times. That&#39;s why, whether you&#39;ve had a miscarriage in the past, are in treatment or thinking about your first cycle, we offer regular webinars to support, advise and empower you, in addition to your friendly Patient Coordinator.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="color:#203240"><strong>When choosing a fertility clinic, it is important to consider several key factors.</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Please confirm whether the clinic offers a range of fertility treatments and assessments.<br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Have you found a medical professional whose skills and expertise match your needs? Can they address your concerns and goals, and answer any of your questions? Please confirm whether the clinic is easily accessible.<br />\r\n<span style="color:#e72254">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Does the clinic have access to the latest technology, including laboratory equipment?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="color:#203240">Why our Clinic should be your first choice</span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Our approach is women-centric, delivering improved health outcomes for both mothers and babies. Our innovative approach prioritizes the quality of eggs over the quantity.<br />\r\nWe are committed to promoting gentler fertility treatment, which we believe provides women with the best chance of success and reduces the emotional, physical, and financial burden associated with IVF.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src="data:image/png;base64," /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Remember, every fertility journey is unique, just like you!<br />\r\nThe first step is to have a consultation with a fertility specialist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href="https://drsagiroglu.com/en/contact/"><span style="font-size:20px"><em><strong><span style="color:#203240">Get in touch with us today.</span></strong></em></span></a></p>	1		\N	\N
